title: Match history on web is blank page
body:
Match history on web doesn't show anything, it's been two weeks. how to solve?
Thanks.

replies.body:
https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous/th9befm3-there-is-a-extension-that-fixes-league-website-white-box-match-history-glitchbug

@Porocles, or any riot team member, if you can maybe look into this extension and how it fixes this match history problem, that would be great
It Worked! Thank u so much!

I clicked on your match history, and everything looks fine.  Make sure that you're selecting the right URL, but here it is just in case:

http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history/NA1/231976037

If you still run into any issues, try clearing your [cache and cookies](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) to make sure the page will load up to date info.  I hope that helps!
